snippet.title: Dhanda Nyoliwala - Not Guilty (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
‚ÄúNot Guilty‚Äù is the Tenth song from Dhanda Nyoliwala‚Äôs album. The track reflects real-life struggles, false blame, loyalty, and inner strength. With powerful Haryanvi lyrics, Dhanda talks about standing firm when the whole world is against you. Raw emotions, street reality, and faith in family make this song deeply relatable.

snippet.title: Bal Thackeray (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Amar Karnawal | New Haryanvi Song 2026
snippet.description:
Bal Thackeray (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Amar Karnawal | New Haryanvi Song 2026

NRI29 Productions bring you new haryanvi song 2026 in the voice of Masoom Sharma, penned by Amar Karnawal. Music produced by Pinna Music and Video shot by Chand Shivraj.

Song  - Bal Thackeray
Title - Bal Thackeray
Singer- Masoom Sharma 
Artists- Masoom Sharma 
Writer - Amar Karnawal 
Music - Pinna Music 
Composition- Masoom Sharma
Director- Chand Shivraj
Editor - Monty
DOP - Sushil 
Poster Design- B Town Graphics 
Project By - Vikas Rajana 
Producer- Sahab Bishnoi 
Label- NRI 29 Productions 
Special Thanks Haryanvi Association of Western Australia, Nven Verma , Anmol Rajput , Aman Sharma and Kiru 

Distribution Partner & Management : Ziaan Entertainment FZCO


Lyrics 

Mathe tika, aankh pe chasma

Kadd aur kaathi bhi s gach

Arre muh pe kehna, sukh t rehna

Saari bol chora sach

302 mai naam rahe se,
Maare aval kaam rahe se
376 lagdi dekhi s tere barge jaar ke

Re jor javani, dor tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chal bukal maarkay

jor javani, dor tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maarkay

Arey mar jau mitarr k khaatir
Pehla s yo karam mera
Arey hindu jaat aur chatri kom s, satya sanatan dharam mera

Vo bhagwa sujay raam n pujay
Charche saare yar ke gunjay
Bhagat singh se mohar lage maare kirdaar kay

Re jor javani, torr tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maarkay

jor javani, dorr tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maar key 

Arey Karanawalia chaam paad dye
Bhidne ka sahas na kr 
Chaanan bargi zindagi jee
Isne kaali umaavas na kr 
Re tere kuch be konya kisa 
Amar toh nyu hi lega jee sa 
Laage minute ka chotha hisa 
Dhar dyu chaati paad ke 

Re jor javani, torr tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maarkay

On our channel we create –∞ trailer mashups ‚ñ∑
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and Add Our Own Dialogues To Make A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot ocr genre of the film entirely.

This video is a parody DUE to its derivative/ transformative nature this video is covered as a Fair Use of material.

snippet.title: Rishtey (Official Music Video) | Jass Bajwa | Punjabi Song 2026
snippet.description:
Jass Bajwa presents the official music video of Rishtey. It is a touching Punjabi song that shows the deep bond between a daughter and her family. As she gets ready to leave her parents‚Äô home after marriage, memories of childhood, siblings, and family moments come rushing back.

The song captures her love, fear, and pain of leaving the house where she grew up. She remembers small fights, shared laughter, and the comfort of seeing her parents every day. Before starting her new life, she makes emotional requests to her brother and sister, showing how strongly she is connected to her family. Rishtey beautifully reflects love, memories, and the strength it takes to move forward while keeping family close to the heart.

snippet.title: Toxic Yash Teaser Trailer REVIEW | NAMAN SHARMA
snippet.description:
#TheReviewPoint


Rocking Star Yash is back, and this time it‚Äôs not about mass hysteria or KGF-style nostalgia.
The TOXIC teaser is a calculated, controlled, and deeply unsettling cinematic statement that feels more like a warning than a promotion.

In this video, we break down TOXIC from a pure movie critic‚Äôs perspective ‚Äî focusing on visual grammar, sound design, character psychology, director Geethu Mohandas‚Äô intent, and why this teaser has already started shaking the industry.

This is not fanboy hype.
This is cinema analysis ‚Äî sharp, ruthless, and honest.

Watch till the end to understand:
* Why TOXIC is not trying to please everyone
* How Yash is repositioning himself post-KGF
* Why silence in this teaser is louder than BGM
* What the teaser hides ‚Äî and why that matters

üëâ This is not a review. This is a reality check.

Bruno Mars is a 16x GRAMMY¬Æ-winning global superstar, singer, songwriter, multi-instrumentalist, producer, and one of the most-streamed artists in the world. Known for his showmanship and chart-toppers, Bruno has set a number of records throughout his career, including becoming the first artist ever to hit 150 million monthly listeners on Spotify, appearing on two of the fastest songs to reach one billion streams (for ‚ÄúDie with a Smile‚Äù with Lady Gaga and ‚ÄúAPT.‚Äù with ROS√â, and achieving the highest-certified song in RIAA history with 2010‚Äôs ‚ÄúJust the Way You Are‚Äù). Since launching a string of hits beginning in 2009, Bruno has sold over 150 million records worldwide, making him one of the best-selling artists of all time. Beyond his work as a soloist, Bruno is a member of the duo Silk Sonic with Anderson .Paak. In addition to his 35 Billboard Hot 100 hits, including nine number one singles, Bruno is the recipient of 16 GRAMMY¬Æ Awards (including ‚ÄúAlbum of the Year‚Äù for 24K Magic), 14 American Music Awards, and seven MTV Video Music Awards. His 24K Magic World Tour was among the highest-grossing tours in history, and within the top ten highest-grossing of the 2010s.

Ces vid√©os consistent √† collecter des extraits de films issus d'un ou plusieurs longs m√©trages et √† les monter pour cr√©er une nouvelle bande-annonce. Ces ≈ìuvres d√©riv√©es peuvent b√©n√©ficier de la protection du droit d'auteur au titre de l'exception de citation ou de parodie. Les mashups de bandes-annonces ne sont pas seulement une forme de cr√©ativit√© num√©rique g√©n√©r√©e par les utilisateurs, mais aussi un moyen de susciter l'attente autour des sorties de films √† venir, en compl√©ment des bandes-annonces existantes. Ces derni√®res sont con√ßues pour d√©voiler un minimum d'√©l√©ments de l'intrigue et cr√©er l'engouement et l'attente. Les mashups r√©alis√©s par les fans permettent au public de proposer sa propre interpr√©tation cin√©matographique des images du film. Movie: a sublime love story- Barsaat (2005)
Featuring: Bobby Deol, Priyanka Chopra, and Bipasha Basu
Song: Saajan Saajan Teri Dulhan Sajaoongi 
Singers: Alka Yagnik, Kailash Kher
Music: Nadeem Shravan
Lyrics: Sameer
Produced & Director: Suneel Darshan
Production : Shree Krishna International

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - Trailer 4 "The Wakandans & The Fantastic 4 Will Return" | Marvel Studios
snippet.description:
‚Äî Attention Viewers ‚ö†Ô∏è
‚Äî This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
‚Äî Avengers: Doomsday - The Wakandans & The Fantastic 4 Will Return

‚Äî This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support ‚Äî now let‚Äôs dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. üé¨‚ú®

‚Äî In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story shifts toward legacy, duty, and the consequences of survival as Shuri carries the weight of a world that has taken everything from her. Having lost her family, her king, and her past, she steps fully into her role not just as Black Panther, but as a leader navigating the fragile balance between nations shaped by grief and power. Her path intersects with Talokan, where Namor stands as a reminder that kings are defined by the burdens they accept, not the battles they fight. As Wakanda looks beyond its borders, a historic meeting finally comes to pass with the Fantastic Four, signaling alliances forged across generations and timelines. The trailer positions these converging forces as essential players in the coming conflict, framing Avengers: Doomsday as a story about responsibility inherited, choices made in silence, and the fragile unity required to prevent the collapse of everything that remains.
